{"tid":1691993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沙田再有五星旗遭示威者棄置侮辱","createTime":"2019-11-04T01:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T02:01:23.000Z","uid":56881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f45e36b80595aaf054b994dfbcdf546b14ea7d32","tid":1691993,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:27:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%94%E6%98%9F%E6%97%97%E9%81%AD%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%A3%84%E7%BD%AE%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1-214500450.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%2597%2597%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%25A3%2584%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E4%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BE%25B1-214500450.html&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=03d30739\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%94%E6%98%9F%E6%97%97%E9%81%AD%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%A3%84%E7%BD%AE%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1-214500450.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nZgkMECmr6hCIQXxGtRHuQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/e3771e44633debb6f50ba7dbcc46c514\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnZgkMECmr6hCIQXxGtRHuQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fe3771e44633debb6f50ba7dbcc46c514&h=8e2c5d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田有五星旗被棄置在草叢。（李浮南攝）<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】沙田再有五星旗被示威者棄置。逾百名示威者昨午近四時聚集在沙田新城市廣場中庭呼叫「五大訴求、缺一不可」等口號，突然有一名黑衣男子把五星旗拋棄在地上後離去，惟在場人士並無理會。約數分鐘後，一名灰衣男子檢起地下五星旗，一路步行到地下巴士站，並把五星旗棄置在巴士站近公路附近的草叢後離開。<br />\n<br />\n疑從沙田大會堂拆去<br />\n<br />\n昨有過百名反修例網民在沙田新城市廣場發起「行街」活動，期間有人把國旗棄置在路邊草叢。記者昨午五時許曾折返沙田大會堂三支旗杆處查看，但不見任何旗幟懸掛，其中一支杆則有旗繩。現場消息指，沙田大會堂昨日曾升起五星旗，有職員對五星旗「消失」感驚訝，但未知被示威者棄置在草叢的五星旗是否從大會堂拆去。<br />\n<br />\n係護旗手呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地先最鍾意當國旗係垃圾咁掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d31e7ec6441019251c9ea1fe5b0ed681268a2f3","tid":1691993,"uid":1387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f0b63c60f2c98047e49eb1c2c6513386ea546fa","tid":1691993,"uid":320680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:29:12.000Z","msg":"今次689出幾錢？"},{"pid":"493961b2ed7a6a066081f617da3cf4ef6745f898","tid":1691993,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:01:23.000Z","msg":"十四億護旗手去左邊?<br />\n咁多人都睇唔住支旗?<br />\n應該每支旗派10隻護旗手24小時看守啦"}]}